Bibliographic References: PP, no. 66, pi. lANon Sepcifiedd; PPSupp, no. 100; Schauenburg, RM 79, 1972, pi. 14.
Imagery Description: (a) Draped woman bending forward with phiale and wreath in 1. hand, fillet in r., Dionysos with thyrsus; small stele between them, and above, a female bust, (b) Air, with strigil, + Br, with strigil; both with sticks.
